column5: Have a look at Tylers Auction items , new items are being added almost daily . A good cause and some awesome items to be bid on.  TB

Thanks for bumpin a reminder Dave!  Come'on folks...lets see the same OFC spirit we had last year. Bid hard and bid often. Remember.....This isn't Ebay where you wait to the last minute to pounce for a dollar......
I'm hoping that Maureen puts up the Pete Maina video, book and gift certificate.
Take a look there is even 'free 'delivery on some items ! TB
I want the fish fryer when it gets posted and if anyone out bids me I am going to come and get you!!!!!!!!

don't worry Roger I will , I just need a few minutes to do it...I'm hoping by tomorrow night I'll have the rest up...  Cliff, you need to talk to Roy....maybe he bought it himself  I'll see about extending the auction a few days to make up for the lateness of posting some of the items.  Right now I'm going to bed  Maureen
